c0 ls0 ws0">hands over their mouths and chant, &quot;Unclean, unclean.&quot; </div><div class="t md27 x73 h87 ya9c ff1 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The horror of the crowd. </div><div class="t mf2f x99 h27 ya9c ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;He is a loathsome spectacle. The disease </div><div class="t md2 x71 h27 yb8e ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">has made frightful inroads, and his decaying body is horrible to look upon. </div><div class="t m1160 x71 h27 ybc1 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">At the sight of him the people fall back in terror. They crowd upon one </div><div class="t mb5a x71 h27 y2030 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">another in their eagerness to escape from contact with him. Some try to </div><div class="t m1369 x71 h27 y1410 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">prevent him from approaching Jesus, but in vain. . . . He sees only the Son </div><div class="t m143b x175 h87 y1214 ff1 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">35 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
